Class MappedDictionary

java.lang.Object
  com.dhemery.configuring.MappedDictionary
All Implemented Interfaces:
StringDictionary
public class MappedDictionary
extends Object
implements StringDictionary

A dictionary stored in a Map. Changes to the dictionary are written through to the underlying map. Entries in the underlying map are reflected in the dictionary.
